quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  44,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  44,1,h m
  44,2,qasam hai iss kitaab Mubin ki
  44,3,"ke hum ne isay aik barri kher o barket wali raat mein nazil kya hai, kyunkay hum logon ko mutnabba karne ka iradah rakhtay thay"
  44,4,yeh woh raat thi jis mein har maamla ka hakeemana faisla
  44,5,hamaray hukum se sadir kya jata hai hum aik rasool bhejnay walay thay
  44,6,tairay rab ki rehmat ke tor par yaqeenan wohi sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
  44,7,asmano aur zameen ka rab aur har uss cheez ka rab jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hai agar tum log waqai yaqeen rakhnay walay ho
  44,8,koi mabood uss ke siwa nahi hai wohi zindagi ataa karta hai aur wohi mout deta hai tumhara rab aur tumahray unn islaaf ka rab jo pehlay guzar chuke hain
  44,9,( magar fi al waqea inn logon ko yaqeen nahi hai ) balkay yeh apne shak mein parre khail rahay hain
  44,10,acha intzaar karo uss din ka jab aasman Sarih dhuwan liye hue aeye ga
  44,11,"aur woh logon par chhaa jaye ga, yeh hai dard naak saza"
  44,12,"( ab kehte hain ke )"" parvar-digaar, hum par se yeh azaab taall day, hum imaan laatay hain """
  44,13,inn ki ghaflat kahan daur hoti hai? inn ka haal to yeh hai ke inn ke paas rasool Mubin aa gaya
  44,14,"phir bhi yeh uss ki taraf multafit nah hue aur kaha ke"" yeh to sikhaya parhaya bawla hai """
  44,15,"hum zara azaab htaye dete hain, tum log phir wohi kuch karo ge jo pehlay kar rahay thay"
  44,16,jis roz hum barri zarb lagayen ge woh din hoga jab hum tum se intiqam len ge
  44,17,hum inn se pehlay firaon ki qoum ko isi azmaish mein daal chuke hain unn ke paas aik nihayat shareef rasool aaya
  44,18,"aur is ne kaha"" Allah ke bundon ko mere hawalay karo, mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon"
  44,19,Allah ke muqablay mein sar kashi nah karo mein tumahray samnay ( apni mamoriyat ki ) Sarih sanad paish karta hon
  44,20,aur mein apne rab aur tumahray rab ki panah le chuka hon iss se ke tum mujh par hamla aawar ho
  44,21,"agar tum meri baat nahi mantay to mujh par haath daalnay se baz raho """
  44,22,aakhir kaar uss ne apne rab ko puraka ke yeh log mujrim hain
  44,23,( jawab diya gaya ) acha to raton raat mere bundon ko le kar chal par tum logon ka peecha kya jaye ga
  44,24,samandar ko uss ke haal par khula chore day yeh sara lashkar ghark honay wala hai
  44,25,""" kitney hi baagh aur chashmay"
  44,26,aur khait aur shandaar mehal thay jo woh chore gay
  44,27,"kitney hi aish ke sir o samaan, jin mein woh mazay kar rahay thay unn ke peechay dharay reh gay"
  44,28,"yeh howa unn ka injaam, aur hum ne dosaron ko inn cheezon ka waris bana diya"
  44,29,"phir nah aasman unn par roya nah zameen, aur zara si mohlat bhi un ko nah di gayi"
  44,30,iss terhan bani Israel ko hum ne sakht zillat ke azaab
  44,31,firaon se nijaat di jo hadd se guzar jaane walon mein fi al waqea barray ounchay darjay ka aadmi tha
  44,32,"aur unn ki haalat jantay hue, unn ko duniya ki doosri qomon par tarjeeh di"
  44,33,aur unhen aisi nishanain deikhein jin mein Sarih azmaish thi
  44,34,yeh log kehte hain
  44,35,""" hamari pehli mout ke siwa aur kuch nahi uss ke baad hum dobarah uthaye jaane walay nahi hain"
  44,36,"agar tum sachey ho to utha lao hamaray baap dada ko """
  44,37,yeh behtar hain ya tba ki qoum aur uss se pehlay ke log? hum ne un ko isi bana par tabah kya ke woh mujrim hogaye thay
  44,38,yeh aasman o zameen aur inn ke darmain ki cheeze hum ne kuch khail ke tor par nahi bana di hain
  44,39,"inn ko hum ne brhq peda kya hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  44,40,inn sab ke uthaye jaane ke liye tey shuda waqt faislay ka din hai
  44,41,"woh din jab koi Aziz qareeb apne kisi Aziz qareeb ke kuch bhi kaam nah aeye ga, aur nah kahin se inhen koi madad puhanche gi"
  44,42,"siwaye iss ke ke Allah hi kisi par reham kere, woh zabardast aur Raheem hai"
  44,43,zaqoom ka darakht
  44,44,gunah gaar ka khaja hoga
  44,45,"tail ki tilchat jaissa, pait mein iss terhan josh khaye ga"
  44,46,jaisay kholta howa pani josh khata hai
  44,47,""" pakro isay aur rageedtayhu-ay le jao iss ko jahannum ke bichon beech"
  44,48,aur undail do iss ke sir par kholtey pani ka azaab
  44,49,"chakh is ka maza, bara zabardast izzat daar aadmi hai too"
  44,50,"yeh wohi cheez hai jis ke anay mein tum log shak rakhtay thay """
  44,51,khuda taras log aman ki jagah mein hon ge
  44,52,baghoon aur chashmo mein
  44,53,"Hareer o Deeba ke libaas pehnay, aamnay samnay baithy hon ge"
  44,54,yeh hogi un ki shaan aur hum gori gori aho chasham aurtain un se bayah den ge
  44,55,wahan woh itminan se har terhan ki lazeez cheeze talab karen ge
  44,56,"wahan mout ka maza woh kabhi nah chakhain ge, bas duniya mein jo mout aa chuki so aa chuki aur Allah apne fazl se ,"
  44,57,un ko jahannum ke azaab se bacha day ga yahi barri kamyabi hai
  44,58,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne iss kitaab ko tumhari zabaan mein sahal bana diya hai taakay yeh log nasiyaat haasil karen"
  44,59,"ab tum bhi intzaar karo, yeh bhi muntazir hain"
